title: Honey BBQ Chicken with Coconut Rice, Crisp Slaw & Aioli
description: This smokey and sticky delight uses barbecue seasoning and honey to coat baked chicken breast for abundant flavours you can only dream of. Serve with a bed of creamy coconut rice and crunchy slaw for a crave-worthy dinner that's as pretty as a picture.

